title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update - Cessna Citation CJ4 & Avionics
description:
In this video we will have a look at the changes to the Cessna CJ4 aircraft and to the avionics inside the aircraft which received a large update as part of AAU 1. This update is still in beta but works pretty well for a beta on my machine. We will go a little bit from change to change (and sometimes back ;-)).
